Class EnumRegistry<T extends ExtensibleEnum<T>>

java.lang.Object
org.jscience.util.EnumRegistry<T>
public class EnumRegistry<T extends ExtensibleEnum<T>> extends Object
Registry for ExtensibleEnum values.

Manages registration and lookup of enum-like values, supporting both built-in and user-defined values.
